"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-09-02-Olympians-from-Chinese-mainland-attend-gala-in-Macao-SAR-1wyUTPrLFoQ-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Athletes of Chinese mainland attended a gala on Sunday night during their three-day visit to south China's Macao Special Administrative Region.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"score\": 0.9917249230068197, \"rank\": 0.008344125272188925, \"text\": \"Chinese mainland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\"}, {\"begin\": 326, \"end\": 331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5441406704325871, \"rank\": 0.5823937354432286, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 334, \"end\": 339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macau\", \"score\": 0.9999953370545003, \"rank\": 4.637393961469223e-06, \"text\": \"Macao\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the theme \\\"Our pride,\\\" the gala was made up of three parts: \\\"Surpass your dream,\\\" \\\"Break the limit\\\" and \\\"Build your future dream.\\\"\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympians not only participated in performances on the stage, but also shared their experience and stories of making the country proud.\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wasn't fighting alone because our great country had my back,\\\" 2024 Paris Olympic Games gold medalist swimmer Pan Zhanle said.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 773, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My gold medal is a gift to our country.\\\"\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We finished the final with a draw in regular time,\\\" said Chinese women's hockey player Li Hong.\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 875, \"end\": 882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.8604915501958359, \"rank\": 0.15635974179100545, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 905, \"end\": 912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li_Hong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.927688971121183e-16, \"text\": \"Li Hong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li_Hong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li_Hong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Though we lost in the penalty shootout, we received applause from the opponents' supporters when we traveled around the stadium wearing the Chinese national flags.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1055, \"end\": 1077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_China\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chinese national flags\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's when I realized that we had gained respect after displaying the spirit of Chinese athletes.\\\"\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1160, \"end\": 1167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.8604915501958359, \"rank\": 0.15635974179100545, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the mixed doubles event requires good coordination and communication,\\\" champion paddler Sun Yingsha said.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yingsha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sun Yingsha\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13382519\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yingsha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yingsha\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We needed to adapt ourselves quickly to the changes in every game.\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was happy that me and Wang Chuqin could win the event in Paris.\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1387, \"end\": 1398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Chuqin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wang Chuqin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13382519\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Chuqin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Chuqin\"}, {\"begin\": 1422, \"end\": 1427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999717431369, \"rank\": 2.8256826672490605e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to thank you for your support.\\\"\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Eating good food in Macao helped a lot to release my pressure,\\\" Chinese table tennis team captain Ma Long said.\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1490, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macau\", \"score\": 0.9999953370545003, \"rank\": 4.637393961469223e-06, \"text\": \"Macao\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macau\"}, {\"begin\": 1534, \"end\": 1541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.8604915501958359, \"rank\": 0.15635974179100545, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1568, \"end\": 1575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ma_Long\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ma Long\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13382519\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ma_Long\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ma_Long\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He recommended pineapple buns to visitors.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There were a series of interesting programs at the gala.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1682, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, one was to have paddlers and shuttlers using the others' gear to compete in a contest of hitting cups on the table.\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Table tennis players also played a match on a randomly moving table.\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": []}]